*   **Proposed Fix:** Always use a static format string and pass the variable data as an argument.

```c
void log_request(const char *user_agent) {
    char msg[256];
    snprintf(msg, sizeof(msg), "request from %s", user_agent);
    syslog(LOG_INFO, "%s", msg); // Fixed: Added %s format specifier
    printf("%s", msg);           // Fixed: Added %s format specifier
    printf("\n");
}
```

